description:
http://anidb.net/ch6383 [Momomiya Ichigo] is just an ordinary 13-year-old girl until a bizarre incident occurs at a museum during her first date. The accident, which merges her DNA with that of a wildcat`s, is actually part of the µ Project to protect the Earth from danger.
Momomiya Ichigo, code name http://anidb.net/ch6384 [Mew Ichigo] (Strawberry), along with four other chosen girls: http://anidb.net/ch6386 [Mew Mint] (http://anidb.net/ch6385 [Aizawa Mint]), http://anidb.net/ch6388 [Mew Lettuce] (http://anidb.net/ch6387 [Midorikawa Lettuce]), http://anidb.net/ch6390 [Mew Pudding] (http://anidb.net/ch6389 [Fong Pudding]) and http://anidb.net/ch6392 [Mew Zakuro] (http://anidb.net/ch6391 [Fujiwara Zakuro]) now have to protect the Earth and learn about their mysterious enemy using the Cafe Mew Mew as their base of operations.
